{"segment":2,"line_start":101,"line_end":200,"dialogues":[{"speaker":"char_rui_wei","speaker_name":"芮玮","listener":null,"text":"吾命休矣！","tone":"恐惧","chapter":4,"line_start":109,"line_end":110},{"speaker":"char_rui_wei","speaker_name":"芮玮","listener":"char_xun_shi_nv","text":"多谢姑娘救命，在下感激不尽！","tone":"认真","chapter":4,"line_start":123,"line_end":124},{"speaker":"char_xun_shi_nv","speaker_name":"驯狮女","listener":"char_rui_wei","text":"你是谁？","tone":"疑问","chapter":4,"line_start":127,"line_end":127},{"speaker":"char_rui_wei","speaker_name":"芮玮","listener":"char_xun_shi_nv","text":"在下天池府简召舞。","tone":"认真","chapter":4,"line_start":129,"line_end":129},{"speaker":"char_xun_shi_nv","speaker_name":"驯狮女","listener":"char_rui_wei","text":"你不是简家的大公子！","tone":"认真","chapter":4,"line_start":133,"line_end":133},{"speaker":"char_rui_wei","speaker_name":"芮玮","listener":"char_xun_shi_nv","text":"怎么不是？","tone":"慌张","chapter":4,"line_start":135,"line_end":135},{"speaker":"char_xun_shi_nv","speaker_name":"驯狮女","listener":"char_rui_wei","text":"简家大公子在天池府是有名的驯狮能手，你要是他，怎会有今日之难？","tone":"认真","chapter":4,"line_start":137,"line_end":138},{"speaker":"char_rui_wei","speaker_name":"芮玮","listener":"char_xun_shi_nv","text":"我真是简家的大公子呀！","tone":"无奈","chapter":4,"line_start":141,"line_end":142},{"speaker":"char_xun_shi_nv","speaker_name":"驯狮女","listener":"char_rui_wei","text":"这里的狮子十分凶野，你无驯狮的技能，不要再来！","tone":"温柔","chapter":4,"line_start":145,"line_end":146},{"speaker":"char_rui_wei","speaker_name":"芮玮","listener":"char_xun_shi_nv","text":"谢谢你！","tone":"认真","chapter":4,"line_start":149,"line_end":150},{"speaker":"char_xun_shi_nv","speaker_name":"驯狮女","listener":"char_rui_wei","text":"不用！","tone":"淡然","chapter":4,"line_start":153,"line_end":153},{"speaker":"char_rui_wei","speaker_name":"芮玮","listener":"char_xun_shi_nv","text":"请问姑娘芳名？","tone":"好奇","chapter":4,"line_start":155,"line_end":155},{"speaker":"char_xun_shi_nv","speaker_name":"驯狮女","listener":"char_rui_wei","text":"我的名字不能告诉你。","tone":"淡然","chapter":4,