{"segment":3,"line_start":201,"line_end":300,"dialogues":[{"speaker":"char_rui_wei","speaker_name":"芮玮","listener":null,"text":"这么晚了，怎么还没有睡？","tone":"疑问","chapter":4,"line_start":249,"line_end":249},{"speaker":"char_qiu_shu","speaker_name":"秋书","listener":"char_rui_wei","text":"奴婢见公子没睡，自个便睡不稳，特为您煮于一杯莲子汤，来服侍您！","tone":"娇声","chapter":4,"line_start":251,"line_end":252},{"speaker":"char_rui_wei","speaker_name":"芮玮","listener":"char_qiu_shu","text":"早不是吩咐你们，不要再来服侍？","tone":"冷酷","chapter":4,"line_start":255,"line_end":256},{"speaker":"char_qiu_shu","speaker_name":"秋书","listener":"char_rui_wei","text":"我深夜起来为您煮了一杯，您就吃了吧！","tone":"娇声","chapter":4,"line_start":259,"line_end":260},{"speaker":"char_qiu_shu","speaker_name":"秋书","listener":"char_rui_wei","text":"公子，我好久没有服侍你了……","tone":"娇声","chapter":4,"line_start":269,"line_end":269},{"speaker":"char_rui_wei","speaker_name":"芮玮","listener":"char_qiu_shu","text":"滚开！","tone":"愤怒","chapter":4,"line_start":273,"line_end":273},{"speaker":"char_rui_wei","speaker_name":"芮玮","listener":"char_qiu_shu","text":"你再不走，我就刺你！","tone":"冷酷","chapter":4,"line_start":277,"line_end":278},{"speaker":"char_qiu_shu","speaker_name":"秋书","listener":"char_rui_wei","text":"公子……你怎么啦？","tone":"惊讶","chapter":4,"line_start":281,"line_end":282},{"speaker":"char_rui_wei","speaker_name":"芮玮","listener":"char_qiu_shu","text":"人不能无耻，你快离开，好自反省，尔后我也不记着今夜之事！","tone":"严肃","chapter":4,"line_start":285,"line_end":286},{"speaker":"char_rui_wei","speaker_name":"芮玮","listener":"char_qiu_shu","text":"快走！快走！莫惹我火了！","tone":"愤怒","chapter":4,"line_start":291,"line_end":293},{"speaker":"char_qiu_shu","speaker_name":"秋书","listener":"char_rui_wei","text":"我的假公子，你回过头来说话！","tone":"嘲讽","chapter":4,"line_start":295,"line_end":295},{"speaker":"char_rui_wei","speaker_name":"芮玮","listener":"char_qiu_shu","text":"你……你……说什么？","tone":"恐惧","chapter":4,"line_start":299,"line_end":299},{"speaker":"char_qiu_shu","speaker_name":"秋书","listener":"char_rui_wei","text":"我们姐妹四人正奇怪公子的性情怎么变了，没想到变成一个道学