{"segment":4,"line_start":301,"line_end":400,"dialogues":[{"speaker":"char_qiu_shu","speaker_name":"秋书","listener":"char_rui_wei","text":"我的意思吗？哼！我的意思要你以后什么都要听我的暗中指挥！","tone":"冷酷","chapter":4,"line_start":307,"line_end":308},{"speaker":"char_rui_wei","speaker_name":"芮玮","listener":"char_qiu_shu","text":"我是天池府的公子，怎么能听你一个奴婢的命令？","tone":"愤怒","chapter":4,"line_start":311,"line_end":311},{"speaker":"char_qiu_shu","speaker_name":"秋书","listener":"char_rui_wei","text":"你还敢自称公子？公子好淫成性，我的清白就坏在他手上，却不是你这个假道学！","tone":"冷酷","chapter":4,"line_start":313,"line_end":314},{"speaker":"char_rui_wei","speaker_name":"芮玮","listener":"char_qiu_shu","text":"你要怎样？","tone":"无奈","chapter":4,"line_start":317,"line_end":317},{"speaker":"char_qiu_shu","speaker_name":"秋书","listener":"char_rui_wei","text":"你只要听我的命令，我便不拆穿你的身份：","tone":"冷酷","chapter":4,"line_start":321,"line_end":321},{"speaker":"char_pan_zhong_xu","speaker_name":"潘中虚","listener":"char_rui_wei","text":"公子到哪里去了？","tone":"冷酷","chapter":4,"line_start":367,"line_end":367},{"speaker":"char_rui_wei","speaker_name":"芮玮","listener":"char_pan_zhong_xu","text":"外面现在怎么样了？","tone":"冷酷","chapter":4,"line_start":371,"line_end":371},{"speaker":"char_pan_zhong_xu","speaker_name":"潘中虚","listener":"char_rui_wei","text":"老奴不知，待老奴前去照应。","tone":"平静","chapter":4,"line_start":383,"line_end":383},{"speaker":"char_pan_zhong_xu","speaker_name":"潘中虚","listener":"char_rui_wei","text":"公子开门！公子开门！","tone":"冷酷","chapter":4,"line_start":389,"line_end":391},{"speaker":"char_rui_wei","speaker_name":"芮玮","listener":"char_pan_zhong_xu","text":"又有什么事？","tone":"冷酷","chapter":4,"line_start":393,"line_end":393},{"speaker":"char_pan_zhong_xu","speaker_name":"潘中虚","listener":"char_rui_wei","text":"老奴特来禀告外面没事了！","tone":"冷酷","chapter":4,"line_start":395,"line_end":395},{"speaker":"char_rui_wei","speaker_name":"芮玮","listener":"char_pan_zhong_xu","text":"还有什么事，快快说出！","tone":"冷酷","chapter":4,"line_start":397,"line_end":397},{"speaker":"char_pan_zhong_xu","speaker_name":"潘中虚","lis